trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> class represents a configuration set for one or more AD LDS instances.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> 類別表示一個或多個 AD LDS 執行個體的組態集。

trans-unit.source: Demand value: <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityAction.LinkDemand" />
trans-unit.target: 要求值： <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityAction.LinkDemand" />

trans-unit.source: Gets a read-only collection of AD LDS instances that are in the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 取得組態集中 AD LDS 執行個體的唯讀集合。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstanceCollection" /> object that contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> objects that are in the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstanceCollection" /> 物件，其中包含在組態集中的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: Gets a read-only collection of application partitions that are in the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 取得在組態集中的應用程式磁碟分割的唯讀集合。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartitionCollection" /> object that contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> objects that are in the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartitionCollection" /> 物件，其中包含在組態集中的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: Releases the resources that are used by the object.
trans-unit.target: 釋放物件所使用的資源。

trans-unit.source: Releases all managed and unmanaged resources that are used by the object.
trans-unit.target: 釋放此物件所使用的所有 Managed 和 Unmanaged 資源。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> value that determines if the managed resources should be released.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> 值，可決定是否應該釋放 Managed 資源。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the managed resources should be released; <see langword="false" /> if only the unmanaged resources should be released.
trans-unit.target: 如果應該釋出 Managed 資源，則為 <see langword="true" />；如果應該只釋出 Unmanaged 資源，則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the object and optionally releases managed resources.
trans-unit.target: 釋放由此物件所使用的 Unmanaged 資源，並選擇性地釋放 Managed 資源。

trans-unit.source: Finds an AD LDS instance in this configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 尋找這個組態集中的 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> object that represents an AD LDS instance that was found.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> 物件，表示找到的 AD LDS 執行個體 (Instance)。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: An AD LDS instance could be not found in this configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 在這個組態集中找不到 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that specifies a partition in which to search.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，指定要搜尋的磁碟分割。

trans-unit.source: Finds an AD LDS instance in this configuration set for a given partition name.
trans-unit.target: 在這個組態集中尋找指定分割名稱的 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> object that represents an AD LDS instance that was found.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> 物件，表示找到的 AD LDS 執行個體 (Instance)。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="partitionName" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="partitionName" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: An AD LDS instance for the specified <paramref name="partitionName" /> could not be found in this configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 在這個組態集中找不到指定之 <paramref name="partitionName" /> 的 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that specifies a partition in which to search.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，指定要搜尋的磁碟分割。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that specifies a site in which to search.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，可指定要搜尋的站台。

trans-unit.source: Finds an AD LDS instance in this configuration set for a given partition name and site name.
trans-unit.target: 在這個組態集中尋找指定分割名稱和網站名稱的 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> object that represents an AD LDS instance that was found.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> 物件，表示找到的 AD LDS 執行個體 (Instance)。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="siteName" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="siteName" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: An AD LDS instance for the specified <paramref name="partitionName" /> and <paramref name="siteName" /> parameters could not be found in this configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 在這個組態集中找不到指定之 <paramref name="partitionName" /> 和 <paramref name="siteName" /> 參數的 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Returns all AD LDS instances in this configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 傳回這個組態集中的所有 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstanceCollection" /> object that contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> objects that were found.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstanceCollection" /> 物件，其中包含已找到的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that specifies a partition in which to search.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，指定要搜尋的磁碟分割。

trans-unit.source: Returns all AD LDS instances in this configuration set for a given partition name.
trans-unit.target: 針對指定的分割名稱，傳回這個組態集中的所有 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstanceCollection" /> object that contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> objects that were found.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstanceCollection" /> 物件，其中包含已找到的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="partitionName" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="partitionName" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that specifies a partition in which to search.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，指定要搜尋的磁碟分割。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that specifies a partition in which to search.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，指定要搜尋的磁碟分割。

trans-unit.source: Returns all AD LDS instances in this configuration set for a given partition name and site name.
trans-unit.target: 針對指定的分割名稱和網站名稱，傳回這個組態集中的所有 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstanceCollection" /> object that contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> objects that are found.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstanceCollection" /> 物件，其中包含找到的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="siteName" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="siteName" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext" /> object that contains the target and credentials to use to retrieve the object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext" /> 物件，其中包含用來擷取此物件的目標和認證。

trans-unit.source: The target of the context can be an AD LDS instance or keywords that are specified in the serviceConnectionPoint object in the current forest that can identify the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 在可識別組態集的目前樹系中，內容的目標可以是 AD LDS 執行個體，或是在 serviceConnectionPoint 物件中所指定的關鍵字。

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> object for the specified directory context.
trans-unit.target: 傳回指定之目錄內容的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> object that represents the configuration set for the specified context.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> 物件，表示指定之內容的組態集。

trans-unit.source: A target specified in the <paramref name="context" /> parameter could not be found.
trans-unit.target: 找不到 <paramref name="context" /> 參數中指定的目標。

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫基礎目錄服務導致發生錯誤。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="context" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="context" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="context" /> parameter is not valid.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="context" /> 參數無效。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry" /> object for the configuration partition.
trans-unit.target: 取得組態分割的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry" /> object for the configuration partition.
trans-unit.target: 組態分割的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Returns the AD LDS replication security level.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 AD LDS 複寫安全性層級。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationSecurityLevel" /> value that indicates the current AD LDS replication authentication mode.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationSecurityLevel" /> 值，表示目前的 AD LDS 複寫驗證模式。

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> 物件的名稱。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，其中包含 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> 物件的名稱。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: Gets the AD LDS instance that is the current owner of the domain naming master role.
trans-unit.target: 取得 AD LDS 執行個體，其為網域命名主機角色的目前擁有人。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> object that represents the AD LDS instance that currently holds the domain naming master role.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> 物件，表示目前持有網域命名主機角色的 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: Gets the schema object for the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 取得此組態集的結構描述物件。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchema" /> object that represents the schema for this configuration set.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchema" /> 物件，表示這個組態集的結構描述。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: Gets the AD LDS instance that is the current owner of the schema operations master role.
trans-unit.target: 取得 AD LDS 執行個體，其為結構描述作業主機角色的目前擁有人。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> object that represents the AD LDS+
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance" /> 物件，表示 AD LDS+

trans-unit.source: instance that currently holds the schema operations master role.
trans-unit.target: 執行個體，此執行個體目前持有結構描述作業主機角色。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationSecurityLevel" /> value to which to set the AD LDS replication authentication mode.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationSecurityLevel" /> 值，要將 AD LDS 複寫驗證模式設定為這個值。

trans-unit.source: Sets the AD LDS replication security level.
trans-unit.target: 設定 AD LDS 複寫安全性層級。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="securityLevel" /> is not a valid <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationSecurityLevel" /> value.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="securityLevel" /> 不是有效的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationSecurityLevel" /> 值。

trans-unit.source: Gets a read-only collection of sites that are in the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 取得在組態集中的站台之唯讀集合。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReadOnlySiteCollection" /> object that contains <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySite" /> objects that are in the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReadOnlySiteCollection" /> 物件，其中包含在組態集中的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySite" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已被處置。

trans-unit.source: Returns the name of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> 物件的名稱。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the name of the current <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，其中包含目前 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet" /> 物件的名稱。
